      <h2>謎の香りはパン屋から</h2>
      <p><strong>Author:</strong> 土屋うさぎ</p>
      <p><strong>Published:</strong> 2025</p>

      <h3>⭐ Review</h3>
      <p><bold>Rating</bold>: ⭐⭐⭐⭐</p>
<p>When I first saw this book, I got intrigued by the word 謎 (Mystery). As I really love any books that have mystery plot or murder mystery, detective related.</p>

<p>Apart from that, I would say it’s an medium pace read, and enjoy reading it from the first page</p>

<p>But this is a different flavor of mystery novel, that leans more on the heartwarming plot that conveys various feelings from 5 different stories.</p>

<p>Warm, friendship, lovers, finding confidence, chasing one’s dream, trust…</p>

<p>And one of the quotes that I love and able to relate to it:</p>
<p>“挑戦することは大変だ。だが人生には、困難に立ち向かい、泣いた経験のある者だけが、知ることのできる〝味〟がある。”</p>
    </article>
